last_episode_to_air.name: Trận chiến cuối cùng
last_episode_to_air.overview: Lord Takeshi kidnapped tje neighboring Princess, believing that her fortune would make the territory prosper. Shakrito and 100 warriors will have to pass through the dangerous challenges created by Lord Takeshi and the two great minions and cunning counselors. The fight to rescue the princess features many dramatic challenges, requires physical strength as well as coordination and solidarity between the warriors to be able to rescue Princess Woonsenko.

name: Takeshi's Castle
overview: Fictional stories combine with interactive television. There is a beginning and an end, but the climax and drama on the journey to rescue the princess will depend complete on the players.
